About

Who We Are

A Portland-based Thai community football club competing in regional friendlies and tournaments in the Pacific Northwest.

Mission

Grow the game, represent our culture, and create a positive space for players and families of all ages.

2026 Objectives

  • Rebrand and relaunch
  • 3 marquee matches (Seattle x2, Labor Day)
  • Fundraise $10,000
